--- MAGISK ANDROID APP FILES ---

This directory is reserved for the future Android application.

Recommended stack:
- React Native / Expo (shared component architecture with web)
- Or Capacitor (wrap web app for native deployment)
- Or Flutter (separate codebase, shared API layer)

The web app is built with responsive design in mind,
using mobile-first breakpoints that map well to native views.

Key considerations:
- Share the same Supabase backend
- Reuse API service layer from src/services/
- Reuse validation schemas from src/validations/
- Reuse TypeScript types from src/types/
